message.body: :) how's your morning going, my love?
Good!! Woke up around 8 for some reason and stayed in bed till now!
Ahah sounds wonderful! Noooot gonna lie, with i was right there with ya! I went to bed at 8...and couldnt sleep! Im too excited to see you. So i gave up haha!
Haha. Soon!!!! Soooo sooooon!
Haha now now now nooooow!!
Sorry baby. Making breakfast. Ha
Haha well ooook. Enjoy!
Good morning, darling!! Hope youre ready for the day! Ive got a huge huge favor to ask tho. Can you call me furiously at 10? I dont want to over sleep!! Thanks!
Okay!!
Thank you, my love! You the best! I cant wait to see you!!
Have a good bus ride :) I go nap now
Interviewer sickly so they rescheduled. Soooo that means, i all yours!! Whatcha wanna do today haha!?
Haha yay!!! No offense to him!
Hehe nope :) I cant say i mind haha. Rescheduling is gonna be a bitch though...since i'll be heading to you next wk
Oh no!!! I'm sorry love.
Is ok! I'll find a day. Nooo worries. You ready to get on the bus?
I'm already on the bus!!! I guess you don't need me to wake you up then
Woohooo!! And...nope haha. Guess its time for breakfast. I was gonna shave and get all fancy for you...sorry baby haha. Guess the hoodie is going back on ha
That's perfectly A-OK! We go back and go to bed! Yeah yeah?
Is you trying to tempt me or something?? With the evils of sleep? Who wants more than 2 hrs of shut eye. Not THIS guy. No way no how. I'll hold you lovingly tho
Haha. Okay. I'll sleep then! I'm watching dr who right now.
Haha and i'll be right next to you, wait til you fall asleep...and then pass out hard. Hope youve got good episodes lined up!
Haha. I do. I do!!
Good! :) Now imma git up, break my fast, make my boday immaculately clean for you and then put on my bestest traveling getup. So so so happy youre on the way :)
Me too!! See you soon!
Love you! Enjoy the show!
